<hymn_number>172</hymn_number>
<title>chuán dào 迦南172</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men de yuàn wàng wǒ men de yuàn wàng wǒ men de yuàn wàng shì chuán dào,
 wǒ men de shǐ mìng wǒ men de shǐ mìng wǒ men de shǐ mìng shì chuán dào
 wú lùn dé shí bù dé shí wù yào chuán dào,
 zǒng yào fàng dǎn bǎ fú yīn jiǎng míng wǒ men yào chuán dào.</lyrics>
</song>